      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "This memo confirms our commitment to robust **regulatory compliance** for the new fintech client, strictly adhering to **anti-money laundering** and **financial crime** statutes. Our **customer due diligence** process mandates comprehensive **identity verification** and thorough **procurement of documents**, including rigorous **verification of identity**. We employ a **risk-based approach**, necessitating **enhanced due diligence** for any client presenting as a **politically exposed persons** or operating from a **high-risk jurisdiction**, alongside mandatory **sanctions screening** and **PEP screening**. Furthermore, we meticulously assess the **ultimate beneficial owner** and **beneficial ownership**, scrutinizing the **source of funds** and **source of wealth** to prevent **terrorist financing** and **combatting illicit finance**, while maintaining **ongoing monitoring** and **fraud prevention** protocols, including **adverse media** checks and **checking against lists** to file a **suspicious activity report** when necessary.",
